  "body": "When a member node receives imported messages via archives, the `getContactDetailsAsJson()` call in `messagesView` keeps performing `getVerificationRequestsFrom()` requests which makes the scrolling experience jittery.\r\n\r\nThe reason this is the case, is that imported messages are signed by the community, so every call to `getVerificationRequestFrom()` results in an empty response. Because there's no in memory verification information, desktop keeps reaching out to statusgo.\r\n\r\nThe solution to that would probably be to avoid checking the `getVerificationRequestFrom()` call when the message in question was signed by the community it belongs to.",
